Did she just leave without saying bye?

29
00:02:32,124 --> 00:02:33,542
I'm sorry, sir.

30
00:02:34,084 --> 00:02:36,128
I asked them to take
special care of your son,

31
00:02:36,212 --> 00:02:38,214
