47
00:03:49,326 --> 00:03:53,998
That I would protect Yeong-ro.

48
00:03:55,541 --> 00:03:56,667
<i>Mom.</i>

49
00:03:58,627 --> 00:04:00,421
I'll protect Yeong-ro.

50
00:04:01,380 --> 00:04:02,673
So don't worry.

51
00:04:03,674 --> 00:04:05,718
I'll make sure she marries

52
00:04:05,801 --> 00:04:07,970
someone who loves her so much.

53
00:04:08,846 --> 00:04:12,808
And I'll look out for her by her side
until she becomes an old lady,

54
00:04:13,392 --> 00:04:15,102
so don't worry about a thing, Mom.

55
00:04:16,270 --> 00:04:18,314
I'm just three years younger than you.

56
00:04:27,614 --> 00:04:28,490
Dad.

57
00:04:29,408 --> 00:04:30,492
Yes?

58
00:04:32,786 --> 00:04:34,204
Yeong-ro…

59
00:04:40,878 --> 00:04:42,421
Keep her safe.

60
00:04:43,505 --> 00:04:44,923
Of course, I will.

61
00:04:45,507 --> 00:04:48,427
But you should get better
and do it yourself.

62
00:04:50,429 --> 00:04:51,764
You should do that.

63
