Come on, do something!

74
00:05:15,579 --> 00:05:16,789
Yeong-u, wake up!

75
00:05:17,498 --> 00:05:20,501
Wake him up!

76
00:05:21,668 --> 00:05:24,421
Don't fall asleep! Yeong-u!

