on the West Sea around 22:00 last night,</i>

82
00:08:43,453 --> 00:08:47,332
<i>Eun Yeong-u, the son of the ANSP director,
was injured and passed away.</i>

83
00:08:47,416 --> 00:08:51,378
<i>It has been known that the person KIA
was corporate Kim Seong-hun,</i>

84
00:08:51,461 --> 00:08:54,631
<i>but it turned out
that it was marine Eun Yeong-u,</i>

85
00:08:54,715 --> 00:08:56,842
<i>the ANSP director's son, that died.</i>

86
00:08:56,925 --> 00:08:59,011
<i>What's more shocking is that Lim Soo-ho,</i>

87
00:08:59,094 --> 00:09:01,805
<i>the leader of the spies
who killed Eun Yeong-u,</i>

88
00:09:01,888 --> 00:09:05,809
<i>is holding the students hostage
in Hosu University dorm as we speak.</i>

89
00:09:05,892 --> 00:09:09,313
<i>He'd been acting secretly
all over East Germany,</i>

90
00:09:09,396 --> 00:09:12,691
<i>but he disguised himself as an economics
graduate student at Berlin University</i>

91
00:09:12,774 --> 00:09:14,610
<i>and came to Korea</i>

92
00:09:14,693 --> 00:09:17,362
<i>to approach Professor Han I-seop.</i>

93
00:09:17,654 --> 00:09:21,241
<i>This is the shocking truth revealed a day
after the engagement on the West Sea.</i>

94
00:09:21,325 --> 00:09:24,244
<i>We will update you
as soon as we find out more.</i>

95
00:09:44,431 --> 00:09:45,432
What…

96
00:09:46,683 --> 00:09:48,185
What did she just say?

97
00:09:53,106 --> 00:09:54,399
My brother…

98
00:09:56,860 --> 00:09:58,195
was killed?

99
00:10:09,790 --> 00:10:12,250
My brother is dead?

100
00:10:22,469 --> 00:10:23,470
No…

101
00:10:26,973 --> 00:10:28,100
No…

102
00:10:28,767 --> 00:10:29,810
No…

103
00:10:30,727 --> 00:10:32,479
It can't be true.

104
00:10:34,272 --> 00:10:36,942
Why… Why is my brother dead?

105
00:10:37,025 --> 00:10:37,984
No…

106
00:10:39,486 --> 00:10:40,737
That's not true…

107
00:10:45,367 --> 00:10:47,953
Yeong-u… Yeong-u!

108
00:10:52,124 --> 00:10:54,126
Yeong-u… Yeong-u!

109
00:10:54,209 --> 00:10:55,127
Eun Yeong-ro!

110
00:10:56,294 --> 00:10:57,129
Eun Yeong-ro!

111
00:11:00,340 --> 00:11:01,508
-Yeong-ro!
-Yeong-u!

112
00:11:03,385 --> 00:11:06,388
Let go! Let go of me!

113
00:11:06,972 --> 00:11:08,056
Calm down!

114
00:11:09,850 --> 00:11:11,768
I need to go see for myself!

115
00:11:15,355 --> 00:11:17,482
It's dangerous.
You don't want to die, do you?

116
00:11:45,677 --> 00:11:47,637
You're the leader of those
who killed Yeong-u?

117
00:11:48,805 --> 00:11:50,557
You evil bastard.

118
00:11:50,640 --> 00:11:53,435
Holding us hostage wasn't enough?
Why did you kill my brother?

119
00:11:53,518 --> 00:11:55,187
What did he do wrong?

120
00:11:55,270 --> 00:11:57,481
He didn't do anything to deserve it!

121
00:12:00,066 --> 00:12:01,401
Bring him back.

122
00:12:02,110 --> 00:12:03,904
Bring him back!

